.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-PIN-SET" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-pin-set \- set a PIN for the wallet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-pin-set
.I wallet_name pin
.SH DESCRIPTION
Stores a SHA-256 hash of the provided PIN in the wallet's meta table.
.PP
Output: JSON object with ok and wallet fields.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-pin-reset (1)
